BootstrapStat - Class in entity
A class which contains validated data from the CSV files

correctRows - ArrayList<String[]> of validated records in the CSV file
bootstrapErrors - ArrayList<BootstrapError> of errors in the CSV file
fileName - Name of CSV file
numRecords - number of correct records in the CSV file
rowNum - HashMap<String,Integer> for UserLocationController, rowNum is a hashmap for containing the timestamp + macaddress and the row number of that particular row to check for duplicates
BootstrapStat() - Constructor for class entity.BootstrapStat

correctRows - ArrayList<String[]> of validated records in the CSV file
bootstrapErrors - ArrayList<BootstrapError> of errors in the CSV file

numRecords - number of correct records in the CSV file

key - timestamp + macaddress
value - row number of CSV file
